devdoc.author: Dilum Bandara, CSIRO's Data61

addFriend(address,string).details: To simplify the code duplication of friends is not checked --> now implemented with friendAlreadyExists modifier

returns._0: Number of friends added so far

addRestaurant(string).details: To simplify the code, duplication of restaurants isn't checked --> now implemented with restaurantAlreadyExists modifier

returns._0: Number of restaurants added so far

doVote(uint8).details: To simplify the code duplicate votes by a friend is not checked --> now implemented with votedAlready modifier

returns.validVote: Is the vote valid? A valid vote should be from a registered  friend to a registered restaurant

devdoc.title: Contract to agree on the lunch venue
